# FieldBourne Digital marketing site

Read `AGENTS.md` and `README.md` before making changes.

## What this repo is

Static marketing site (HTML/CSS/JS, no bundler). Deployed from repo root via GitHub Pages. Product app lives in [tv-magic-companion](https://github.com/missbeardy/tv-magic-companion) — link only, do not embed app code here.

## Key files

- `assets/site-config.js` — `formEndpoint`, `tvmagicAppUrl`, `contactEmail`, `siteUrl`
- `assets/styles.css` — brand tokens (`--teal`, `--amber`, `--dark`, `--bg`)
- `assets/site.js` — contact form + homepage ticker

## When editing

- Match existing page structure (nav, footer, font links, `styles.css`).
- Use config for external URLs; avoid duplicating `hello@fieldbournedigital.com.au` or app URLs.
- Australian English, trade-business tone, no generic SaaS jargon.
- Minimal scope: no new frameworks, build tools, or dependencies unless explicitly requested.
